name: [Guest User] Verify successful PayPal account login from the Payment and Order Review page

steps.name: And a product with "Ship to Me" delivery option is added to the cart
And the user has proceeded with the checkout process
When the user selects the PayPal payment method in the payment review page
Then the user should be logged in successfully to the PayPal account
And the user should land on the order confirmation page post PayPal payment
